Sentencas: The performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells was investigated as the SDC buffer layer thickness was varied between similar to 0.4 mu m and similar to 2.3 mu m.
Titulo: Performance variation with SDC buffer layer thickness

Sentencas: The thickness of the buffer layer has a significant effect with the peak performance varying in magnitude by a factor of almost three.
Titulo: Performance variation with SDC buffer layer thickness

Sentencas: A peak power density of 1106 mW cm(-2) was achieved at 800 degrees C and an optimal SDC buffer layer thickness of similar to 1.5 mu m.
Titulo: Performance variation with SDC buffer layer thickness

Sentencas: The performance variation was complex due to a balance between ohmic and polarization losses, triple phase boundary area, pin holes and interfacial reactions between the BSCF + SDC cathode, SDC buffer layer, and YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Performance variation with SDC buffer layer thickness

Sentencas: Understanding this variation is essential in order to compare two fuel cells having a different porous buffer layer thickness.
Titulo: Performance variation with SDC buffer layer thickness
